<title>msẖ rạḥ nskt</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (msẖ rạḥ nskt whạntklm .. rạḥ nʿln myn hw yswʿ
 wbtsbyḥnạ ạlkl yslm .. ạ̹n ạlạ̉rḍ dy mlk yswʿ)2
 ạlqrạr- (ạsmḥ rby wạmlk fynạ
 wfy tsbyḥnạ ạskn yạ mhwb
 ạ̹ʿln qwẗ mlkk bynạ
 qwẗ dmk wạlmṣlwb)2
 2- (ạ̹nt yạ rb fyk kfạytnạ .. ạ̹nt msyḥnạ mlk ạlkwn
 ạ̹nt hdfnạ wkl gẖạytnạ .. mhmạ qạblnạ mʿạk hạyhwn)2
 3- (rạḥ nʿln ạ̹nk yạ qạỷdnạ .. fy ḥrwbnạ gẖạlb wqdyr
 msẖ mmkn yqdr ygẖlbnạ .. ạ̹blys mhmạ ḥạrbnạ ktyr)2
 4- (rạḥ nhtf wngẖny ạ̉gẖạny .. nfrḥ byk wạlfrḥ ydwm
 nfrḥ byk yạ ạ̹lhnạ ạlgẖạly .. nʿln nṣrnạ byk ạlywm)2</lyrics>
</song>